## 5) Draft Engine Rules (v1)

### Inputs

* prior published schedules
* roster
* location membership
* role eligibility
* employee status
* approved time off
* structured availability if present
* max weekly hours if present
* min rest hours if present
* manager preferences if present

### Constraints hierarchy

1. Hard constraints

   * employee active
   * employee assigned to location or eligible there
   * role eligible
   * not on approved time off
   * no overlapping assigned shifts
2. Soft constraints

   * preferred hours
   * fairness distribution
   * historical pattern consistency
   * minimize overtime risk
   * honor manager favorites / priority staff

### Outputs

* assigned shifts
* open shifts
* conflict summary
* recommendation summary for SMS and web

