## 6) Import Rules

### Fatal import blockers

* no valid date parsing for required shift rows
* no valid start/end time parsing for majority of shift rows
* missing required fields after mapping
* corrupt file / unsupported file format

### Warning-level issues

* bad employee email
* malformed phone number
* unknown role value
* unassigned employee name match failure
* duplicate employee candidates
* shift without assignee

### Partial import behavior

* successful rows commit
* warning rows commit where safe
* failed rows move to Action Needed queue
* manager can publish only after required fatal issues are resolved for the relevant schedule window

